{"tid":2440452,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"無哂動力了","createTime":"2021-03-10T03:21:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T03:40:28.000Z","uid":389493,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cb5ac4cc99a1eedb8adafb8684fa8df741e4ff80","tid":2440452,"uid":389493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T03:21:53.000Z","msg":"無哂動力認識新女仔了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前試過太多嘞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除左洗左好多錢之外，最後一個都無留底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家自己遇到困難，無一個會番黎關心我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁又係嘅，我咁廢，咁垃圾，咁失敗，<br />\n佢地要出面嘅渣男都好過要我，寧願俾人係出面傷害都唔會要我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔想再去同新女仔溝通嘞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n世界根本無屬於我嘅兩情相悅<br />\n只有單戀<br />\n做一個廢男真係乜用都無，唔值得任何人鐘意<br />\n繼續係自己狗竇入面，有一日過一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"580158910e5a6cd0741d9ed2fbddce99faf6d526","tid":2440452,"uid":191453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T03:31:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sz9kCFc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsz9kCFc.jpg&h=3f0f447b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36ad91fe1e4ac862aca3436f9beae71b184faedb","tid":2440452,"uid":232594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T03:40:28.000Z","msg":"試下識番個男仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}